windowised nicovideo player (wnp) is a User JavaScript for Opera (or Firefox or other).
This script can play niconico douga with popup window, supports playlist, etc. 

--
This script work on 
  Opera 10.x (main browser)
  Firefox 3.x
  Google Chrome 3.x
  Safari 4.x
  ie 8.x
--

"nicovideo_wnp.js" and "nicovideo_wnp.user.js" are the same files.
